desc: Boutique desert and aquatic plants. Cactus, succulents, plants, painted pots, epoxy resin pots, pots and matching paintings, and more! We're a husband and wife team who love collecting plants and running our little backyard nursery.

layout.text: We're a husband and wife team who love plants of all kinds, but especially cactus! We've built a desert botanical garden in our backyard and we're so happy to share our passion with you ♥
